 "html": "<p>Om jou eie mayonnaise te maak is so bevrydend.  Dis iets wat vinnig en maklik is om te maak.. Sorg dat die bestandele nie te koud is nie.  Haal die eiers uit die yskas voor die tyd.</p>\n<p>BESTANDELE:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>3 eiergele<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MAYONAISE-011.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1566\" alt=\"MAYONAISE 011\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MAYONAISE-011-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>10 ml dijonmostert</li>\n<li>5 ml suiker<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MAYONAISE-019.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1568\" alt=\"MAYONAISE 019\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MAYONAISE-019-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>10 ml witwynasyn of suurlemoensap<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MAYONAISE-013.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1567\" alt=\"MAYONAISE 013\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MAYONAISE-013-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>300 ml carnola olie</li>\n<li>3 ml sout</li>\n<li>knippie peper</li>\n</ul>\n<p>NOU:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>klits alles behalwe die olie saam vir so 20 sekondes in die voedselverwerker<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MAYONAISE-006.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1564\" alt=\"MAYONAISE 006\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MAYONAISE-006-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>voeg nou die olie in n dun straaltjie, regtig baie stadig by  &#8211; dit moet baie stadig gebeur &#8211; die mengsel raak dik.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MAYONAISE-042.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1572\" alt=\"MAYONAISE 042\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MAYONAISE-042-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>skep in bottels en bere in die yskas.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MAYONAISE-036.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1573\" alt=\"MAYONAISE 036\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MAYONAISE-036-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a><a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MAYONAISE-022.jpg\"><br>\n</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Jy kan die mayonnaise geur met:</p>\n<p>knoffel, ansjovis, pesto of vars kruie.</p>\n<p>Nooit weer sal winkelmayonnaise so lekker soos jou eie mayonnaise smaak nie.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MAYONAISE-036.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1573\" alt=\"MAYONAISE 036\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/MAYONAISE-036-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>",
